HEADWORD: Actinium
<hw>Ac*tin"i*um</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <?/, <?/,
ray.]</ety> <fld>(Chem.)</fld> <def>A supposed metal, said by Phipson to
